### 패턴 1: 단위 시스템

```rust
struct Meter(f64);
struct Kilogram(f64);
struct Second(f64);

fn velocity(distance: Meter, time: Second) -> f64 {
    distance.0 / time.0
}
```

### 패턴 2: ID 분리

```rust
